OL,3,CRussian strikes on Odesa kill two
OL,4,Cahead of Orthodox Easter ceasefire
OL,6,FRussian drone strikes killed at least
OL,7,Ftwo people in the Ukrainian city of
OL,8,FOdesa overnight into Saturday, local
OL,9,Fauthorities reported, ahead of a
OL,10,Fproposed ceasefire for Orthodox Easter.
OL,12,FA further two people were wounded in
OL,13,Fthe attack on the Black Sea port city,
OL,14,Fwhen drones hit a residential area,
OL,15,Fdamaging apartment buildings, houses
OL,16,Fand a kindergarten.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/6
