OL,3,CRussian strikes on Odesa kill two
OL,4,Cahead of Orthodox Easter ceasefire
OL,6,FAccording to the Ukrainian Air Force,
OL,7,FRussia targeted Ukraine with 160
OL,8,Fdrones overnight, of which 133 were
OL,9,Fshot down or intercepted, hours before
OL,10,Fa proposed Easter ceasefire was due to
OL,11,Fcome into force.
OL,13,FRussia's Defence Ministry said 99
OL,14,FUkrainian drones were shot down
OL,15,Fovernight across Russia and occupied
OL,16,FCrimea.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/6
