OL,3,CRussian strikes on Odesa kill two
OL,4,Cahead of Orthodox Easter ceasefire
OL,6,FRussian President Vladimir Putin on
OL,7,FThursday declared a 32-hour ceasefire
OL,8,Fover the Orthodox Easter weekend,
OL,9,Fordering Russian forces to halt
OL,10,Fhostilities from 4pm on Saturday until
OL,11,Fthe end of Sunday.
OL,13,FUkrainian President Volodymyr
OL,14,FZelenskyy said on Friday that Ukraine
OL,15,Fis ready to mirror any ceasefire
OL,16,Fsteps, having earlier proposed to
OL,17,FRussia a pause in attacks on each
OL,18,Fother's energy infrastructure over the
OL,19,FOrthodox Easter holiday.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/6
