OL,3,CRussian strikes on Odesa kill two
OL,4,Cahead of Orthodox Easter ceasefire
OL,6,FKremlin spokesman Dmitry Peskov on
OL,7,FFriday described Putin's move as a
OL,8,F"humanitarian" gesture, but said
OL,9,FMoscow remains focused on a
OL,10,Fcomprehensive settlement based on its
OL,11,Flongstanding demands ` a key sticking
OL,12,Fpoint that has prevented the two sides
OL,13,Ffrom reaching an agreement.
OL,15,FA possible prisoner exchange over the
OL,16,FEaster holiday has also been discussed.
OL,18,FRussia's human rights ombudswoman
OL,19,FTatyana Moskalkova said last week that
OL,20,Fboth sides were working on exchanges
OL,21,Fof prisoners.
